OL,3,CCommunity group raise concerns on
OL,4,Cpolicing of new 20mph speed limits
OL,6,FA community group say they have
OL,7,Fconcerns with how the new 20mph speed
OL,8,Flimit will be policed in Langholm.
OL,10,FA 20mph speed limit is being
OL,11,Fintroduced across Langholm with the
OL,12,Faim to make roads safer and create a
OL,13,Fbetter experience for people in the
OL,14,Farea, beginning on 28 March 2025.
OL,16,FTransport Scotland aims to implement
OL,17,Fmore 20mph speed limits across
OL,18,FScotland as part of its national
OL,19,Ftransport strategy.
