OL,3,CCommunity group raise concerns on
OL,4,Cpolicing of new 20mph speed limits
OL,6,FBilly Young, Vice-Chair of the
OL,7,FLangholm Alliance, said: "There is a
OL,8,Fdefinite need to try and control the
OL,9,Fspeed at the top of the town, at the
OL,10,FLondon Bridge, because we do find a
OL,11,Flot of wagons coming round there - at
OL,12,Fquite a speed. But my main concern
OL,13,Fwith it is who is going to police
OL,14,Fthis."
OL,16,FThe speed limit changes result from
OL,17,Fdecisions made at a Dumfries and
OL,18,FGalloway Council Communities Committee
OL,19,Fin December 2021.
