OL,3,CCommunity group raise concerns on
OL,4,Cpolicing of new 20mph speed limits
OL,6,FElizabeth Wilson, owner of The Paper
OL,7,FShop, says she does not know what
OL,8,Fbenefits it will bring. She said: "I
OL,9,Fthink it's going to have to be one of
OL,10,Fthose things where we're going to see
OL,11,Fwhat will happen. Is it going to
OL,12,Faffect the businesses in any way?
OL,13,FPeople might not stop because they're
OL,14,Fnot sure of where they can stop, and
OL,15,Fwhere they can park. They need more
OL,16,Fsignposts."
