OL,3,CCommunity group raise concerns on
OL,4,Cpolicing of new 20mph speed limits
OL,6,FThe local authority say the new change
OL,7,Fwill make local "streets more
OL,8,Fattractive". Councillor Ian Blake,
OL,9,FChair of the Economy and
OL,10,FInfrastructure Committee, said: "A
OL,11,F20mph speed limit for Langholm will
OL,12,Fnot only reduce vehicle speeds and
OL,13,Fcollisions but will also make the
OL,14,Froads and streets more attractive and
OL,15,Fsafer for active travel and vulnerable
OL,16,Fuser groups.
