OL,3,CCommunity group raise concerns on
OL,4,Cpolicing of new 20mph speed limits
OL,6,F"In many places, inappropriate speeds
OL,7,Fcan make travel hazardous where people
OL,8,Flive, work and play ` particularly for
OL,9,Fvulnerable road users such as children
OL,10,Fand elderly people."
OL,12,FCllr Jackie McCamon, Vice-Chair of the
OL,13,Fcommittee, said: "We hope that the new
OL,14,Fblanket 20mph limit in Langholm will
OL,15,Fencourage more people to walk, cycle
OL,16,For wheel. Our local towns and villages
OL,17,Fshould be places where people are free
OL,18,Fto travel in ways that are safe,
OL,19,Fsustainable, healthy and fair."
