OL,3,CCommunity group raise concerns on
OL,4,Cpolicing of new 20mph speed limits
OL,6,FA temporary 20mph speed limit is also
OL,7,Fbeing introduced by Transport Scotland
OL,8,Fon the A7 road that goes through the
OL,9,Ftown, initially in place for 18 months.
OL,11,FA decision on whether to permanently
OL,12,Fintroduce the policy will be made
OL,13,Fafter analysis of traffic data surveys.
OL,15,FFurther changes to the road network
OL,16,Fwill mean renewed yellow lines and
OL,17,Fdifferent waiting restrictions at
OL,18,FStation Buildings and south of the
OL,19,FThomas Telford bridge.
